00:12:47,352 --> 00:12:48,611
vos iz vos tsu redn?

183
00:12:49,393 --> 00:12:56,103
do zits ikh un mayn froy zol zayn gezunt, ho'mir borekhashem zeyer a fayn lebn tsvishn undz.

184
00:12:56,785 --> 00:13:03,107
