00:13:25,287 --> 00:13:32,503
un dos iz mayn zun, Avrom Moyshe un zayn vayb do, mit di ale kinderlekh. zoln zayn gezunt.

189
00:13:32,779 --> 00:13:35,321
zey voynen in Amerike, in Boro-Park.

190
00:13:36,357 --> 00:13:42,291
mayn zun er iz a groyser talmed-khokhem, er hot geshribn a seyfer oyf hilkhes ribes,

191
00:13:42,803 --> 00:13:51,335
zeyer an ongezeener mentsh, un git a sakh LECTURES, oyf toyre.

192
00:13:55,763 --> 00:14:02,135
